            </a>
          </div>

          <!-- Closure panel: values MUST be filled only after you close (local + remote==local) -->
          <div class="panel" aria-label="Closure facts (static)">
            <h2>CLOSURE FACT (STATIC)</h2>
            <pre class="mono"><code>AS_OF_KST: TBD-YYYY-MM-DD
LOCAL_FILE: index.html
LOCAL_LINES: TBD
LOCAL_SHA256: TBD

PREFLIGHT: PASS/FAIL (record after run)
SCRIPT: bin/ev424_pages_preflight_gate_*.sh --include index.html

PREVIEW_URL: TBD
MAIN_URL: TBD

REMOTE_SHA256_PREVIEW: TBD
REMOTE_SHA256_MAIN: TBD
CLOSURE: PASS/FAIL (remote==local)</code></pre>
            <p class="hint">FACT-only: fill values only after you close via terminal (no remote fetch on page load).</p>
          </div>
        </section>

